i\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"手磨好平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"屋企用 開french press<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想買個平平地既磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"French press識沖都可以沖到靚啡<br />\n精品post嗰邊唔建議用Hario，因為磨出嚟啲粉粗幼唔平均，令到沖嘅啡有時苦有時酸 (仲有香港Hario賣得特別貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n百貨公司二三百用刀片嗰啲電磨正確嚟講係碎豆機，原理同食物處理機差唔多，一樣有Hario粗幼唔勻嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n靚入門級手磨要去精品post睇，不過有人推薦C40嘅話唔駛理<br />\n個磨靚還靚，非精品豆本身風味唔明顯，用C40磨粉沖出嚟都唔會變到精品咖啡咁好飲<br />\n真係諗住入精品咖啡坑唔再返轉頭先考慮C40<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b557626505741313cf98704d46a3d548b6d69e45","tid":2118650,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bf7eca3cc97f6c042f4ce85bbf3b0b393200711","tid":2118650,"uid":68389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e08a08ca15299c319f4a29fffe1859fdd6676269","tid":2118650,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c768fc38a371cbb04cb1d0fed923aa38079dbc7","tid":2118650,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"686ea99e8d5b21afb77febb06a59e4895f5d56ec","tid":2118650,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"凍齋啡冇糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:00:18.000Z","msg":"凍嘅ok，熱唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"我熱齊啡都唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:05:58